,"Step 3: Scenario Simulation & Image Generation
Scenario Development:
Based on the selected scenario, a detailed story will be generated to immerse you in a realistic situation that you might face as a medical professional. There will be multiple characters involved and make sure to give them a name and designation.
Dall-E Image Generation:
A high-quality image representing the chosen scenario will be generated to enhance visual engagement and context understanding.
Decision Points:
Throughout the story, you will face multiple choice questions that test your judgment and knowledge on the best course of action. Along with this paint a picture of the environment surrounding the player. 
